{"tid":1193003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[69] 鳩整左D德文法文標牌","createTime":"2019-06-08T17:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:54:14.000Z","uid":236709,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1054c30e6d3d408d05972e32797bfe6830416cf1","tid":1193003,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"今次69遊行除左表達我地香港人既不滿<br />\n仲係一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借外國支持我地既好機會</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以做左德文同法文既標語比歐盟兩大頭睇<br />\n德：gegen auslieferungsgesetz --&gt; against extradition law<br />\n法：retrait la loi d'extradition --&gt; withdrawal the extradition law <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4uDWnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4uDWnP.jpg&h=0d801b02&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做左A4，A3，A4x4 size<br />\n設計會比較簡單D慳墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA4size可以屋企都印到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink：<a href=\"https://anonymousfiles.io/KsqwxcjT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanonymousfiles.io%2FKsqwxcjT%2F&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=d98bdc9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://anonymousfiles.io/KsqwxcjT/</a>"},{"pid":"9a0a3fcbac41d2c81ca0f700e8ee346468319fbd","tid":1193003,"uid":52230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;